.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, british, colombian, spanish, chinese, turkish, egyptian
7 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, chinchilla, horse, guinea-pig, goldfish, lizard
 1. the chinese is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the egyptian##1
 4. the colombian is on the left of the turkish##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the spanish is the owner of the horse##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the lizard and the spanish##2
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the british is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | chinese | indonesian | british   | spanish | colombian | turkish |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish     | mouse     | chinchilla | horse   | ferret   | lizard    |

