.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, coffee, cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, japanese, british, german, argentine, spanish
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the japanese##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the german##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the british##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the german##1
 5. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the british is between the person drinking milk and the argentine##2
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the british is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the italian##1
10. the egyptian is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | milk    | cola  | coffee  | soy-milk  | mirinda      | hot-chocolate       | almond-milk |
| Nationality   | german | british | argentine | spanish | egyptian | japanese | italian  |

