.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, blues, hip-hop, soul, country, electronic, ambient
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, boat, tram, trike, taxi, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the taxi is the fan of blues##1
3. the person driving the bus is between the fan of ambient and the fan of jazz##2
4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person driving the boat is the fan of soul##1
9. the fan of country is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | country | jazz | hip-hop | ambient      | blues      | electronic |
| Transport     | boat | quad-bike | snowmobile       | bus | tram | taxi | trike |

