.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, librarian, social-worker, musician, bartender, doctor, analyst
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, golf, basketball, surfing, weightlifting, handball
1. the social-worker is on the left of the analyst##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the bartender##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is surfing and the software-developer##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the doctor is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | bartender | software-developer | musician | doctor | librarian | social-worker     | analyst |
| Sport   | golf   | basketball    | handball    | surfing      | baseball  | water-polo | weightlifting |

