.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, mirinda, almond-milk, water, tea, sprite
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo, lacrosse, sailing, biathlon, badminton, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person drinking water##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | 7up    | almond-milk | mirinda   | tea | sprite    | water |
| Sport      | sailing | basketball | skateboarding    | water-polo | biathlon    | lacrosse | badminton  |

