The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, videographer, teacher, freelancer, architect, bartender, entrepreneur
 1. the architect is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the mechanic is on the left of the teacher##1
 3. the bartender is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the architect is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the videographer is on the right of the bartender##1
 8. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking sprite##2
11. the architect is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | coffee  | milk   | sprite         | tea     | almond-milk              | soy-milk    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | bartender | videographer | architect | freelancer | entrepreneur | mechanic | teacher |

