.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, spy, sports, scientific, documentary, musical
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, airplane, ship, van, snowmobile, boat, car
1. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the car and the person driving the snowmobile##2
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | sports     | documentary | scientific | spy | musical  | zombie |
| Transport     | ship | van | snowmobile   | subway     | car    | airplane | boat   |

