.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, hot-chocolate, water, lemonade, juice, soy-milk
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, rock-climbing, baking, collecting, card-games, writing
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking water is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | sprite  | iced-tea       | soy-milk         | lemonade         | water   | hot-chocolate        | juice |
| Hobby      | writing | rock-climbing | dancing | collecting | drawing | card-games | baking  |

