7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

