.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, adventure, martial-arts, mystery, superhero, romance, fantasy
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, dubstep, rock, classical, funk, soul, gospel
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the fan of electronic##2
 4. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
 5. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
10. the fan of classical is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | disaster | adventure  | superhero   | romance | fantasy | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | gospel       | electronic | rock | soul  | dubstep   | funk   |

