 4. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
